./sdp/verification/t-038@20260416t181925z-verify.md:14:Implementation matches the spec closely. `narrative_envelope.py` defines `ToneVector`, `NarrativeBeat`, and all three public functions (`envelope_for_beat`, `tone_from_narrative`, `beat_from_directive`) as specified. Phase-specific tension shapes are distinct and consistent with the spec's characterizations (Divination: slow rise; Conversation: sustained high; Crystallization: settling). The `recursive_composer.py` integration at line 237–242 correctly replaces `SectionEnvelope()` with `envelope_for_beat(beat_from_directive(...))` using per-section directives from `_production_arc_for_sections()`.
